lead_paragraph: Calling Hillary Rodham Clinton "a war hawk," Sen. Rand Paul says that if the former secretary of state seeks the presidency, some voters will worry that she will get the U.S. involved in another Mideast war.

headline.main: Sen. Rand Paul Calls Hillary Clinton a 'War Hawk'
